en_132235_0	The Controller of Immigration and Emigration was noticed to appear in front of the judiciary regarding the escape of a suspect in the alleged Indo-Lanka kidney racket from the detention camp in Mirihana.
en_132235_1	Chief Magistrate of Colombo, Gihan Pilapitiya ordered the Chief Inspector of Mirihana Police also to appear before an open court.
en_132235_2	The Chief Magistrate also ordered to further remand the seven other suspects until 16 th May.
